s5342: Fifth year: Ping Gong's younger brother Tong killed Xiang Gong and established himself.
s5349: Lu Ding Gong Song first year: Zhao Gong's mourning came from Qian Hou.
s5353: Seventh year: Nang Wa attacked Wu, defeated us at Yu Zhang. Cai Hou came to court.
s5357: Tenth year: paid court to Chu, detained because of the fur coat.
s5361: Sixth year: Chu attacked us, went out to meet them, defeated them, took Chu's Ju Chao.
s5385: Ninth year: Cai Zhao Hou detained three years, got the fur coat, therefore returned.
s5389: Twelfth year: allied with Zi Chang about the fur coat, got to return, went to Jin, requested to attack Chu.
s5396: Fourteenth year: with Jin led the feudal lords to invade Chu.
s5399: Sixth year: Zhou and we led the feudal lords to invade Chu.
s5400: Thirty-first year: Chu Bao Xu requested rescue.
s5401: Tenth year: Wu and Cai attacked us, entered Ying, Zhao Wang fled. Wu Zi Xu whipped Ping Wang's tomb.
s5403: Twenty-ninth year: contended with Cai for precedence.
s5405: Thirteenth year: contended with Wei for precedence. Chu invaded us, Wu allied with us to attack Chu, entered Ying.
s5409: Ninth year: with Cai attacked Chu, entered Ying.
s5413: Fifth year: Yang Hu seized Ji Huan Zi, made alliance with him, released him. Solar eclipse.
s5417: Eleventh year: Qin rescue arrived, Wu left, Zhao Wang re-entered.
s5428: Sixteenth year: because Wang Zi Zhao's followers created disorder, the king fled to Jin.
s5433: Twelfth year: Wu attacked our Fan, Chu feared, moved to Kuai.
